<del rend="strikethrough"><gap reason="illegible"/></del> des vom Stern / . Darvmb <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_130_r3l16">wir ſie beſant / vnd ſie <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> briefe laſſen hören / . vnd ſie <expan>ſprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_130_r3l17">daʒ ſie ew <expan>ſelb<ex>er</ex></expan> darvmb <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchreıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd darauf ein <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_130_r3l18">wöllen / wo wir ew lıeb vnd <expan>fruntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> <expan>beweıſe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>möht<ex>en</ex></expan> . Das </ab>
